metadata.name: Animalia
metadata.description:
May this piece inspire a cosmic consciousness to the wild, knowing we’re all part of the Animalia kingdom, great and small. 

Inspired by night diving and luminescent creatures, this is a reminder that we share a connection to even the most unlikely, surreal organisms living in the sea.

“If there is magic on this planet, it is contained in water.”

- Loren Eiseley

Model: Shelajit
